(31, 5, '2011-09-19 18:30:02', '2011-09-19 18:30:02', 'Having spent a whole month as  ‘MNNITian’  finding out the lecture halls and the laboratories and with SWAGAT to participate in; it felt as if time had never passed faster. Just as I started to ‘make plans’ about studying, came the blow of AVISHKAR.\r\n\r\nWe were briefed about the grand fest as a technical event wherein everyone could show their potential in different areas of engineering. Initially, the whole fest sounded like something that was totally out of the league for beginners like us. Making robots, designing softwares, planning business; these were things that we were ought to do but had never done before. Everyone could participate and the idea of competing in such hi-tech events with the seniors said it all, we stood no chance. However, it was a great relief to know that Avishkar had many events specially meant for the first years and moreover, special considerations would be made for the first years.\r\n\r\nAfter knowing more about the fest through the website and through seniors, we got to know that there is something for everyone in the fest. Even the weakest one could give it a shot. Having given the aptitude tests and taken the classes also helped in concluding that Avishkar is for everyone.\r\n\r\nNow that Avishkar is only a week away, the entire college seems to be drowned in the charm of the fest. It’s great to see all the notice boards filled with notices about the event. Everyone is in a rush to do something noteworthy and the prize money makes the competitions even more attention-grabbing. The hustle for Avishkar that I see now is implanting the idea of this event as a carnival with a technical twist in my mind.\r\n\r\nAfter all the briefing and campaigning, everyone has raised expectations about this fest and I am no exception. I am yet to see the actual magic of Avishkar, and by me I mean all the first year students who have an added curiosity and interest in everything. I am looking forward to the fiesta and wish all the good luck to the participants as well as the organizers, after all, it’s the energetic involvement of both that will make Avishkar 2011 a history.', 'AVISHKAR - Experiences and Expectations', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'avishkar-from-a-first-year-point-of-view', '', '', '2011-09-19 19:05:10', '2011-09-19 19:05:10', '', 0, 'http://172.31.100.16/blog/?p=31', 0, 'post', '', 1),
