('cyberquest', 'Cyberquest', 'cyberquest', 'events', '<h4 align="center">A clarion call to cyber-folks, the time has finally arrived!!! </h4> <br/><br/><br/>  <p align="justify">\r\n<img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/cyberquest.jpg" width="50%" align="left" alt="Cyberquest"></img>\r\n\r\n  The world of hyperlinks, routers, hash-tables and dark terminals beckons you yet again. Conceive, code, compile and consummate to conquer the biggest cyber-crusade. All the Bill Gates and Sally Floyds in the making, a geeky haven awaits you. Unix-lovers, your commitment to the greater good will pave the way for a better world. All hackers, your obsession with unlocking the mysteries will reveal secrets yet untold. Netizens, your zeal to achieve the unimaginable is what you need to survive. Innovators, put your grey-cells to work and lead us to the realms beyond. Binary deities, your belief in the silicon life will face its greatest challenge. Virtual architects, carve a niche for yourself in the kingdom of webs and clouds. Zero in on that sneaky little bug that gives programmers sleepless nights. Visionary thinkers and veteran coders, bring out your shields and swords, its show-time!</p> <br><br><p align="center">Grand Prize for best overall performer in Avishkar among first year male and female MNNIT students: <b>BSA Cycle</b><br>email us at: <b><u><a href="mailto:cyberquest.avishkar2k11@gmail.om">cyberquest.avishkar2k11@gmail.com</a></u></b><br><br> Join Google Group at: <b><u><a href="http://groups.google.com/group/cyberquest2k11" target="_blank">http://groups.google.com/group/cyberquest2k11</a></u></b><br><br />\r\n  <img src="./sponsor/aricent.jpg" align="middle" /></center><br />Aricent Group\r\n</p><br><br><h4 align="center">The Final Result of CyberQuest 2k11</h4> <br><br>\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1">\r\n  <col wid