('kreedomania', 'Kreedomania', 'kreedomania', 'events', '<h4 align="center"><i> Scorch up in the heat of game , hold the hands of your teammates , walk over the defeat of your opponents , Go on a RAMPAGE !!!</h4><br/><br/><br/></h3></i> <p align="justify" > <img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:60px" src="events/kreedomania.jpg" width="50%" align="left" alt="kreedomania"></img>Load up your gadgets for the kreedomania 2k11 , Where one mistake makes a difference. Where one misunderstanding takes out a team. Where it takes more than talent, strategy and hard work to win. It takes P@$$!0N to win!! Welcome to Kreedomania, the cyber-gaming zone of Avishkar 2011. It''s time to unleash the champion in you, to dare to stand the wrath of war, to survive and to win.<br/><br/>  Deadlier then before ...<br/><br/> Faster then before ...<br/><br/> Uglier then before ...<br/><br/>  We guarantee you for the religion which you never have seen before , the followers which worships the mighty . Its not the game that makes the gamer here , its the gamer which makes the GAME !!!<br/><br/>  If you think you have seen us already .....<br/><br/>                                                We havnt even started !!!</p><br /><br />\r\n<p align="center">Grand Prize for best overall performer in Avishkar among first year male and female MNNIT students: <b>BSA Cycle</b><br><br>Email: kreedomania.avishkar2k11@gmail.com</p>\r\n', 1),
('mechrocosm', 'MechroCosm', 'mechrocosm', 'events', '<h4 align="center"> <i> "Brillant Design + Broad experience in environment with problems + Passion = A movement to tackle complex problems with simple technology"</h4><br/><br/><br/></i> <img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:60px" src="http://avishkar.in/events/mechrocosm.jpg"  width="50%" align="left" alt="mechro_image"></img><p align="justify"> The evolution of man since Stone Age to his current position was not a one day''s feat. The process was one of trials and errors and he had to risk a lot in the path of revelation and enlightenment. He might not have been a magician to look into crystal balls and foresee. But one thing is certain... Anything we see in the present would have been impossible without a vision that would inspire and act as a driving force. Man, unquestionably, had such prescience. <br/><br/>Welcome to MECHROCOSM ,where your inventive ideas are most wanted, where you can gauge your creativity and learn to follow your instincts, and see for yourself what wonders you can do when you THINK!..<br/><br/></p><br/><br/><p align="center">Grand Prize for best overall performer in Avishkar among first year male and female MNNIT students: <b>BSA Cycle</b><br><br></p>', 1),
('online_events', 'Online Events', 'online_events', 'events', ' <h4 align="center"> <i> "Engage your Mind,  Expand your Horizons,  Explore your Creativity"</h4><br/><br/><br/></i> <p align="justify" ><img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/puzzlecorner.jpg" width="50%" align="left"  alt="puzzlecorner"></img> It is time to unbind your horizons of thought and logic. This section of Avishkar invites you to give shape to your aptitude skills integrated with in-built logics. There is no techie or geeky stuff involved here, all that is required is sound acumen and levelheadedness. <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/> </p><br/><br/><p align="center">Grand Prize for best overall performer in Avishkar among first year male and female MNNIT students: <b>BSA Cycle</b><br><br></p>', 1),
('home', 'Home', './index.php', '', '<h2>Avishkar ''11</h2> <br /> <br /> <p align="justify">  Over the years, Motilal Nehru National Institute of Technology has identified and inspired young talent and infused in them the spirit to revolutionize the world. Avishkar, one of the largest technological symposiums of the country has kept up this tradition of innovation and breaking unprecedented frontiers. <br /><br /> This three day festival hosted this year from 23rd to 25th September witnesses the conflux of over 6000 enthusiasts hailing from 550 colleges across the nation. It grants these young minds an unparagoned opportunity to showcase their talent and evince their ideas which may lay the groundwork for the next cutting edge technology. <br /><br /> Living up to the name, Avishkar ''11 represents the apogee of science, engineering and path-breaking technology. From guest lectures and paper presentations on one hand to treasure hunts and gaming contests on the other, it plays host to a gamut of activities which push your capacity to ideate, drive your hunger to innovate and challenge your potential to create like never before. Its not just a fest, its a phenomenon! </p>', 1),
