('aeromodelling', 'Aeromodelling', 'aeromodelling', 'events', '<br><br><h4 align="center">Udaan 2</h4><br><br>\r\n<p align="justify"><img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="./events/udaan.jpg" width="90%" align="left" alt="Image is loading...please wait "></img>After huge success of this event in avishkar 2010, this time also its back, to make you feel the rush\r\nof adrenalin. Aeromodelling was always the best adventure sport anyone can do. Although its time\r\ntaking but the pleasure you get when you fly your own hand built plane is priceless. The problem\r\nstatement is made simpler this year but we have also added more fun into it.\r\n<br></p>\r\n<b>Problem Statement:</b><br><br>\r\n\r\nDesign a free flight hand launch glider and tune it for maximum range and time of flight.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Rules:</b><br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Wingspan should be of maximum 500mm.<br><br></li><li>\r\nYou cannot use readymade models, but you can use pre-cut kits.\r\n<br><br></li><li>The point system will be based on Range and Time of flight only.\r\n<br><br></li><li>In case of tie, other factors like design etc can be taken into consideration.\r\n<br><br></li><li>You cannot use launching mechanism. Only hand launch is allowed.\r\n<br><br></li><li>There is no team, participation will be on individual basis.<br><br></li></ul>', 1),
('registration', 'Registration', 'registration', 'hospitality', '<h4>Registration kit will be provided to all outside registered participants</h4>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n<u><bold>On Campus events</bold></u><br /><br />\r\nFor participating in events to be held inside campus  following steps are necessary.<br /><br />\r\n\r\n	1. Register yourself online for Avishkar. <b>Online  Registration is must for participating in any of the event in Avishkar 2011</b>. Click <a href="./register.php">here</a> to register.<br />\r\n	2. Login with your mail-id and password and  register yourself for the events in which you want to participate.<br />\r\n	3. On Campus registration will start from 22<sup>nd</sup> September 2011 evening.<br />\r\n	4. Report to the Help Desk in main building  entrance MNNIT Allahabad for on-campus registration.<br />\r\n	5. <b>You have to bring 3 passport size photographs,  your college I-card with you.</b><br />\r\n	6. The fees for participating in Avishkar 2011 is  as follows:<br />\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Rs 200/- for Avishkar registration<br />\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Rs 500/- for food and accommodation<br />\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Rs 100/- as Caution money which is refundable<br />\r\n	\r\n	7. Once registered you can participate in any of  the events n Avishkar 2011 except workshops for which you have to pay its  registration fee separately.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<u>Online Events</u><br /><br />\r\nFor online events you have to register yourself online for AVISHKAR 2011 and for the event.\r\nYou can then participate in the event.\r\n\r\n</p>', 1),
