('director', 'Director''s Message', './director.php', 'home', '<p align="justify"><img src="./images/director_photo.jpg" width="30%" align="left" border="5px" />It is heartening to see that the  Institute is once again all set to host the mega event of Technological  exhibition &ldquo;AVISHKAR&rdquo;. The event does not require an introduction anymore  because it has already created its own space among similar other events  organized by the leading technological institutions across the country. This  has become possible because of sheer dedication and team work of the budding  engineering/management students of the Institute under the dynamic leadership  of their dons. The spectacular  techno-management festival Avishkar-2011 scheduled to be held during  Sept.23-25, 2011 at MNNIT campus is ready to offer the young talents a platform  to exhibit their inventions and be a part of the technical extravaganza fully  packed with programs ranging from invited lectures, paper presentation to  treasure hunt and gaming contests. So, guys it is the time for you to leave  aside your stereotype course curriculum and grab the opportunity to go  extra-mural and have fun. While showing your talent do not overlook a huge sum  of money waiting for you to be won. I am sure you would not regret being a part  of this event. You will definitely realize that there is so much fun in  scientific and technological innovations.<br><br>\r\n	I take this opportunity to  congratulate the entire team of Avishkar-2011 and the President of Students&rsquo;  Activity Centre (SAC) for working round the clock in order to load the event  with treasures that would unfurl in the evening of Sept 22, 2011.<br><br>\r\n	I wish the event a magnificent success!<br><br>\r\n<strong>P. Chakrabarti</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Director</strong></p>', 1),
