('cyberquest', 'Cyberquest', 'cyberquest', 'events', '<h4 align="center">A clarion call to cyber-folks, the time has finally arrived!!! </h4> <br/><br/><br/>  <p align="justify">  The world of hyperlinks, routers, hash-tables and dark terminals beckons you yet again. Conceive, code, compile and consummate to conquer the biggest cyber-crusade. All the Bill Gates and Sally Floyds in the making, a geeky haven awaits you. Unix-lovers, your commitment to the greater good will pave the way for a better world. All hackers, your obsession with unlocking the mysteries will reveal secrets yet untold. Netizens, your zeal to achieve the unimaginable is what you need to survive. Innovators, put your grey-cells to work and lead us to the realms beyond. Binary deities, your belief in the silicon life will face its greatest challenge. Virtual architects, carve a niche for yourself in the kingdom of webs and clouds. Zero in on that sneaky little bug that gives programmers sleepless nights. Visionary thinkers and veteran coders, bring out your shields and swords, its show-time!</p> <br><br><p align="center">email us at: <b><font color="#FF0000"><u><a href="mailto:cyberquest.avishkar2k11@gmail.com">cyberquest.avishkar2k11@gmail.com</a></u></font></b><br><br> Join Google Group at: <b><a href="http://groups.google.com/group/cyberquest2k11" target="_blank"><font color="#FF0000"><u>http://groups.google.com/group/cyberquest2k11</a></font></font></b></u><br></p>', 1),
('electromania', 'Electromania', 'electromania', 'events', '<h4 align="center">Electronic circuits might have taken a long time to be invented but they certainly did not take a long time to make their presence felt in all walks of life. From small toys to state-of-the-art satellites, everything depends on electronic circuits.</h4><br/><br/><br/><p align="justify"> The  world of  electronics  throws up challenges for the circuit designers of tomorrow. A mind-boggling problem, the brain of an electronics engineer and quick bucks together cook up a perfect electronic recipe.<br/><br/> So , if you have the skills to undertsand what an electronic circuit has to say.If you think your ideas can bring up a change in this world of electronics.<br/><br/> Then ELECTROMANIA is the event which will provide a platform  for all electronics enthusiasts to exhibit their skills and a podium for people to showcase their innovative ideas </p>', 1),
('rasayans', 'Rasayans', 'rasayans', 'events', '<h4 align="center"> 	&ldquo;I  consider nature a vast chemical laboratory in which all kinds of composition  and decompositions are formed. Vegetation is the basic instrument the creator  uses to set all of nature in motion.&rdquo;- Antoine  Lavoisier </h4> <br/><br/><br/> <p align="justify"> 	Rasayans is the event to rear the nascent  initiatives for spread of chemical engineering education and foster the  interest of the budding engineers to become future stalwarts. <br />        A chemical engineer draws  upon the vast and powerfulscience of chemistry to solve a wide range of  problems. The strong technical and social ties that bind chemistry and  chemical engineering are unique in the fields of science and technology and Rasayans  provides the exotic podium to convert raw talent into technocrats of tomorrow.</p>', 1),
('edifice', 'Edifice', 'edifice', 'events', '<h4 align="center" >Civil Engineering is the art of directing  the great sources of Power in Nature for the use and convenience of man,  where Imagination is  necessary as well as scientific knowledge. With our imagination  and knowledge we create a world for the growth of mankind. </h4><br/><br/><br/>  <p align="justify" > <img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/edifice.jpg" width="50%" align="left" alt="edifice"></img>  Edifice  is a civil engineering event which will judge your vision and technical  approach towards the problem, for the betterment of Human Social Need. Engineering problems are under-defined, there are many solutions, good,  bad and indifferent. The art is to arrive at a good solution. This is a  creative activity, involving imagination, intuition and deliberate choice. &nbsp;A good engineer is a person who makes a design that  works with as few original ideas as possible.<br><br></p> <br><br>', 1),
('advisory', 'Advisory Committee', 'advisory', 'contacts', '<br/><br/>  <table width="609" height="262">   <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Ashwarya Pratap Singh</td><td width="4oopx">Nidhi Paliwal</td></tr> <tr height="20px"></tr>  <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Nisheet Tiwari</td><td width="4oopx">Parul Sirohi</td></tr>  <tr height="20px"></tr>  <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Richa Singh</td><td width="4oopx">Sanjeev Tiwari</td></tr>  <tr height="20px"></tr>  <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Sonali Shrivastava</td><td width="4oopx">Tanvi Jain</td></tr>  <tr height="20px"></tr>   <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Pawan Kumar Verma</td><td width="4oopx">Rahul Dasgupta</td></tr>   <tr height="20px"></tr>   <tr height="20px"><td width="4oopx">Richa Agrawal</td><td width="4oopx">Vijay Kumar</td></tr>    <tr height="20px"></tr> </table>', 3),
('kreedomania', 'Kreedomania', 'kreedomania', 'events', '<h4 align="center"><i> Scorch up in the heat of game , hold the hands of your teammates , walk over the defeat of your opponents , Go on a RAMPAGE !!!</h4><br/><br/><br/></h3></i> <p align="justify" > Load up your gadgets for the kreedomania 2k11 , Where one mistake makes a difference. Where one misunderstanding takes out a team. Where it takes more than talent, strategy and hard work to win. It takes P@$$!0N to win!! Welcome to Kreedomania, the cyber-gaming zone of Avishkar 2011. It''s time to unleash the champion in you, to dare to stand the wrath of war, to survive and to win.<br/><br/>  Deadlier then before ...<br/><br/> Faster then before ...<br/><br/> Uglier then before ...<br/><br/>  We guarantee you for the religion which you never have seen before , the followers which worships the mighty . Its not the game that makes the gamer here , its the gamer which makes the GAME !!!<br/><br/>  If you think you have seen us already .....<br/><br/>                                                We havnt even started !!!</p>', 1),
('mechrocosm', 'MechroCosm', 'mechrocosm', 'events', '<h4 align="center"> <i> "Brillant Design + Broad experience in environment with problems + Passion = A movement to tackle complex problems with simple technology"</h4><br/><br/><br/></i> <img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:60px" src="http://avishkar.in/events/mechrocosm.jpg"  width="50%" align="left" alt="mechro_image"></img><p align="justify"> The evolution of man since Stone Age to his current position was not a one day''s feat. The process was one of trials and errors and he had to risk a lot in the path of revelation and enlightenment. He might not have been a magician to look into crystal balls and foresee. But one thing is certain... Anything we see in the present would have been impossible without a vision that would inspire and act as a driving force. Man, unquestionably, had such prescience. <br/><br/>Welcome to MECHROCOSM ,where your inventive ideas are most wanted, where you can gauge your creativity and learn to follow your instincts, and see for yourself what wonders you can do when you THINK!..<br/><br/></p>', 1),
('online_events', 'Online Events', 'online_events', 'events', ' <h4 align="center"> <i> "Engage your Mind,  Expand your Horizons,  Explore your Creativity"</h4><br/><br/><br/></i> <p align="justify" ><img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/puzzlecorner.jpg" width="50%" align="left"  alt="puzzlecorner"></img> It is time to unbind your horizons of thought and logic. This section of Avishkar invites you to give shape to your aptitude skills integrated with in-built logics. There is no techie or geeky stuff involved here, all that is required is sound acumen and levelheadedness. <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/> </p>', 1),
('home', 'Home', './index.php', '', '<h2>Avishkar ''11</h2> <br /> <br />   Over the years, Motilal Nehru National Institute of Technology has identified and inspired young talent and infused in them the spirit to revolutionize the world. Avishkar, one of the largest technological symposiums of the country has kept up this tradition of innovation and breaking unprecedented frontiers. <br /> This three day festival hosted this year from 23th to 26th September witnesses the conflux of over 6000 enthusiasts hailing from 550 colleges across the nation. It grants these young minds an unparagoned opportunity to showcase their talent and evince their ideas which may lay the groundwork for the next cutting edge technology. <br /> Living up to the name, Avishkar ''11 represents the apogee of science, engineering and path-breaking technology. From guest lectures and paper presentations on one hand to treasure hunts and gaming contests on the other, it plays host to a gamut of activities which push your capacity to ideate, drive your hunger to innovate and challenge your potential to create like never before. Its not just a fest, its a phenomenon! ', 1),
