('genesis', 'Genesis', 'genesis', 'events', '<br><br> <h4 align="center">"Great oaks from little acorns grow"</h4> <br><br><br> <p align="justify"> Bringing forth <b>Genesis.....</b><br><br> the biotechnological side of Avishkar with the quizzical tinge of <b>Double helix</b>, <br><br> the thrill of unravelling clues to unlock levels in <b>Cryptochrome</b>, <br><br> the chance to give a lecture of your own rather than being lectured, to present and be presented with new ideas in <b>Clairvoyance</b>....<br><br> <b>Bio-vision</b> for the culmination of the brightest and most ingenious minds and to unleash the creativity of budding biotechnologists....<br><br> the mind boggling <b>Paladin</b> and last but not the least <br><br> <b>Adrenaline Rush</b>, that, believe me, would surely excite your adrenal glands....<br><br>    <b>Genesis</b> promises to excite those neurons.... like never before...!!<br><br> There''s so much in store for those who dare to bash open the door. So what are you waiting for, this is everyone''s chance to Think, Create, Indulge and Discover...!! <br><br> The very sound of this might seem cliched, but the very experience will be of a carnival in short, and that''s a promise...!!<br><br>  So just take the plunge.....<br><br> </p><br><br>  ', 1),
('robomania', 'Robomania', 'robomania', 'events', '<br><br><p align="justify"> <img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/robomania.png" width="30%"  align="left" alt="robomania"></img> <br /><br/>From the age of gladiators, we have gradually moved on to the era of transformers. The world has mechanised so swiftly that the odd feeling of change is virtually undetectable. Man has found his own way of playing God by producing the ultimate creation of all time - a robot.<br /><br/>  If you have a penchant for creating the incipient models of the robotic race which may one day inherit Earth, Robomania is the place where you can prove your indefeasible dominance. New robotic challenges await you<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></p><br/><br/> ', 1),
