('jigyasa', 'Jigyasa', 'jigyasa', 'events', '<h4 align="center">"Millions saw apples fall, but Newton asked why"</h4><br/><br/><br/> <p align="justify">School Bag is a mixed bag of events which aims to bring out the most competitive young talents from school level by infusing in them a spirit of inquisitiveness. The goal is to establish a sound knowledge base and skill set on which students will be able to build as they are exposed to different life experiences.  Jigyasa is designed for the participation of students of Higher Secondary Schools (11-12). The entire class of events will be spread over three days. The events will be held during Avishkar 2011 (23rd to 25th September).<br/><br/><br/></p> ', 1);
