('fpga', 4, 'Judging', '<b>JUDGING CRITERIA :</b><br><br>\r\n<ul><li>Judging will be done by faculty members of Electrical and Electronics department.<br><br></li><li>The teams will be awarded points on the following aspects by the judges:<br><br><ul><li>Design decisions and implementation.<br><br></li><li>Area used (no. of LUTs).<br><br></li><li>Maximum frequency achieved.<br><br></li><li>Presentation and viva.<br><br></li><li>Additional points.</li></ul><br><br><br></li></ul>\r\n<b>Additional features:</b><br><br>\r\n<ol><li>LCD interfacing. The key generated using DH key exchange is to be displayed.<br><br></li>\r\n<li>You can make more than two modules and introduce i/p layer.<br><br></li></ol>', 'y'),
('ea_sports_cricket', 1, 'Introduction', '<h4 align="center">"a long cricket en direct".....<br>\r\nGeez,its not about being a novice or a pro to practice your religion, it''s in your blood only, it''s in the game. Go gentlemen,gear up your thirst but not your credulity...cz game could be over before you know it. </h4><br><br>\r\n<p align="justify">Folks, it''s time to passionately practice your religion. Yup, you got it right. It''s cricket time! Whether it''s that sweetly timed Straight Drive, the perfectly balanced Leg glance,smashing the kookaburras,lofting the dukes, the intense Square-cut, the lethal in-swinging Yorker, the scary Bouncer or the Doosra which you spent countless hours perfecting; All of your zeal, and skill will be tested here!! This is the perfect spot for those eager to despatch the opponent''s deliveries across the fence like a tracer bullet or for those who can''t wait to scare the hell out of the opponent with their fiery spells.<br><br></p>', 'y'),
