('edi_quest', 1, 'Introduction', '<br><br><h4 align="center">An inquisition, an adventurous expedition and a contingency to explore the royal civilian culture to the fullest.\r\nCome be a part of this, be a part and try to accomplish the supremacy of your mind horses...</h4><br><br>\r\n\r\n<p align="justify"><img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/ediquest.jpg" width="50%" align="left" alt="ediquest.jpg"></img>\r\n\r\nThis is an on the spot civil engineering quizzing event.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\r\n', 'y'),
('fading_blue', 1, 'Introduction', '<h4 align="center" >When you''re thirsty, it''s too late to think about digging a well....</h4><br><br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align="justify"><img style=" border-bottom-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid; border-color:transparent; border-width:8px; border-bottom-width:20px" src="events/fading_blue.jpg" width="50%" align="left" alt="fading_blue"></img>\r\nAll u shutterbugs brush your basics......come out with your cameras...........you would have clicked pics for your fun but this time do it for a real cause.......Move your eyeballs around push your tender fingers to capture can of worms ....help your mother earth. Express, evince, analyze, participate and present solution to the current water related issues around and invigorate others to bring about the change..<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n...........BLUE IS FADING<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;     do something before it turns grey.... . . .<br><br>\r\n\r\n       \r\n\r\n\r\n...Come, Capture and Conquer... <br><br>\r\n<b>....ideate ..innovate..create...</b><br><br></p>\r\n', 'y'),
