('netritva', 2, 'Event Format', '<br><br><strong>First step</strong><br><br>\r\nIt will be an elimination round. This stage will be a written round consisting of questions based on picture perception test and psychoanalytical traits on the situations faced in some adverse conditions, demanding leadership insight, action and vision.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Second step</strong><br><br>\r\nIt will be a group activity round where group tasks will be undertaken aimed to evaluate the team building ability towards group dynamics of the participants. The groups will be formed randomly.<br><br>\r\nSelection to the next stage depends upon prior performance and intra team vote out system wherein team members vote out the least influential member of their group. Influential individual performance can lead to a special wild card entry, subject to panelists'' bench decision.<br><br>\r\n<strong>The ultimate step</strong><br><Br>\r\nThis round checks the intellectual, communication & motivating abilities of participants. Individuals will be addressing and motivating a group of people for a predefined cause for a pre-decided time period<br><Br>\r\n', 'y'),
