 Technology, Networks & Communication, Sensors and Control, In-Car Entertainment\r\n <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>SECURITY & RIGHTS MANAGEMENT:</b><br><br> Copy and Redistribution Protection, Intellectual Property, Trusted Computing & Transactions, Biometrics, Encryption, Security, Parental Control, Privacy, Legal and Regulatory Issues, Standards\r\n \r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>ENABLING TECHNOLOGY:</b><br><br> Advanced Semiconductors, High Speed Signals & Interconnects, Algorithms,O/S, Development Tools, Test Equipment, Advanced Displays, Power and Conventional Batteries, Small Fuel Cells, Cost Reduction, Compliance Testing, Recyclable/Green Engineering, Human-Device Interface, Haptics & Gesture, Special-Needs/Assistive Technology<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn wide spectrum electrical and electronic engineering includes following fields of research:<br><br>\r\n\r\n<ol><li>Antennas and Propagation\r\n<br><br></li><li>Bioinformatics and Synthetic Biology\r\n<br><br></li><li>Communication Systems\r\n<br><br></li><li>Digital Signal Processing\r\n<br><br></li><li>Electrical Machines\r\n<br><br></li><li>Electromagnetic Theory\r\n<br><br></li><li>Embedded Systems\r\n<br><br></li><li>Fuzzy Logic and Neural Networks\r\n<br><br></li><li>High Voltage A.C. and D.C Systems\r\n<br><br></li><li>Industrial Control\r\n<br><br></li><li>Instrumentation\r\n<br><br></li><li>Microelectronics\r\n<br><br></li><li>Mobile (Wireless)    Communication\r\n<br><br></li><li>Networks, Circuits and Systems\r\n<br><br></li><li>Non-Renewable Sources of Power\r\n<br><br></li><li>Optical Communication\r\n<br><br></li><li>Power Electronics\r\n<br><br></li><li>Power Quality\r\n<br><br></li><li>Power Security\r\n<br><br></li><li>Power Systems Stability and Control\r\n<br><br></li><li>Sensors and Transducers\r\n<br><br></li><li>Sustainable Transport\r\n<br><br></li><li>Transmission and Distribution of power\r\n<br><br></li><li>Very Large Scale Integration (VLSI)\r\n	<br><br></li></ol>\r\n', 'y'),
