('networking', 1, 'Introduction', 'A workshop on <strong>Server Administration</strong> is being held from 22nd-23rd September as a part of AVISHKAR 2011. The workshop will be taken by NEERAV KUMAR (Alumni 2010 batch and previous   system administrator the college).<br /><br />\r\nThe following topics will be covered during the workshop.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<center><strong><u>Day 1</u></strong></center><br />\r\n<ol type="1">\r\n	<li>Linux file-system structure</li>\r\n	<li>Basic commands: ls, cd, uname, w, last, history, cat, df, du, find, strings</li>\r\n	<li>grep, sed, wc,tr,awk</li>\r\n	<li>SSH: using it, debugging it, using public keys, sshuttle, X tunneling, normal tunneling and finally securing it.</li>\r\n	<li>Linux:   securing it over the terminal, environment variables, important files,   how to check if they have been modified, fork-bomb.</li>\r\n	<li>Routes, Netstat, Nmap, lsof, DNS poisoning, Proxy Servers, Networking</li>\r\n	<li>SMTP. HTTP. why use HTTPS,Telnet, securing mails using DKIM and SPF. DNS, RDNS, GeoIP</li>\r\n	<li>Search vulnerabilities, nikto , get exploit code.</li>\r\n	<li>Google-based Hacking</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n	<br><br />\r\n\r\n<center><strong><u>Day 2</u></strong></center><br />\r\n<ol start="10" type="1">\r\n<li>Settingup various servers Apache, MYSQL, Mail, DNS, redirecting ports and setting up a transparent proxy.</li>\r\n<li>Phishing how to detect it, key-loggers, how to get past key-loggers.</li>\r\n<li>Denial of service attacks, how to do them, how to stop them.</li>\r\n<li>Social Engineering: How does it work? Ways to do it.</li>\r\n<li>Bruteforcing, Rainbow tables, GPU cracking CUDA.</li>\r\n<li>Metasploit, Nmap, Denial-of-service atttacks, how to stop them.</li>\r\n<li>Doubt session, Demos with real sites, hacking responsibly.</li></ol>\r\n<br />\r\n<center><strong>The workshop will be of total 16 hours duration (8 hours each day).</strong></center>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n\r\n<b>Registration Fee</b><br /><br />\r\nFor MNNIT participants  - Rs. 800/-<br />\r\nFor outside participants  - Rs. 1000/-<br /><br /><br />\r\n<b>Contacts:</b><br /><br />\r\n<table>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td width="150px">Deepak Agarwal</td>\r\n		<td width="150px">+91-8004170575</td>\r\n		<td>Patel - 259</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>Payal Tak</td>\r\n		<td></td>\r\n		<td>KNGH - G25</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<br /><br /><br />\r\n<center><strong>Note : The registration will be closed on 21st September 2011 10:00 pm</strong></center>', 'y');
